songs.title: CUT OUT
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
All alone
All alone
Lone, lone
Lone, lone
Lone, lone, lone
All alone
I'm all alone
Lone, lone
Lone, lone
Lone, lone, lone
All alone

[Verse 1]
Last day
We could try now
We could try new way
Run away, fit this town in my suitcase

[Interlude]
Remember your lies

[Verse 2]
Run away, take a long break
From the whole damn thang
I need a change
We could watch the sunset, never dream again
But we lost
Except for what the fuck it was we had

[Chorus]
All alone
All alone
Lone, lone
Lone, lone
Lone, lone, lone
All alone
I'm all alone
Lone, lone
Lone, lone
Lone, lone, lone
All alone

[Outro]
All alone
Lone, lone
Lone, lone
Lone, lone, lone
All alone
I'm all alone
Lone, lone
Lone, lone
Lone, lone, lone
All alone
